latestIgtvVideos.title: #CCisSafe
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We have been taking very strict measures to ensure extremely high level of cleanliness, sanitisation, temperature check measures and contactless delivery reaches your home ! 
Our CC hunger warriors are ensuring this following steps : 
1. Compulsory Usage Of Gloves 
2. Temperature Checks Of Each Staff Member 
3. 20 Sec Hand-wash Pre handling & Post Handling Each Delivery 
4. Deep Sanitising Door Handles, Kitchens, Delivery Pick Up Areas 
5. Ensuring Sanitiser Use To Each Delivery Rider 
6. Contactless Delivery 
Order Now On : 
@zomatoin @swiggyindia

At Coffee Culture we specialise in Medium and Light Roast Coffees.. which brings out the natural notes and sweetness.. telling a story about the place and environment where this coffee is grown.
When you over roast the coffee, it gets burnt and that erases its story.

So our Message is simple:
DONT DRINK BURNT COFFEE!
